reviewText: My grandaughter loved it! It was really great for Easter, all  the grandkids watch it. The Easter bunny watched it!
My grandson loves the Chipmunks.  I didn't know there were themed movies.  I was so excited to get it to put in his Easter basket.

My children and I pretty much enjoy all the chipmunks stuff but this one was disappointing. I thought it would be more Easter stuff but it is one Easter cartoon and then random ones that have nothing to do with Easter. Would not buy or rent this again.

Ok, so I put five stars because my son says he loves it. It has a number of small episodes, but worth it for small children. I do love that it came in two days and was very new. We love Alvin and the chipmunks, so this was a great movie worth the price.
What can I say, Its the Chipmunks! Kids and adults always love them and always will. Mine sure do! Bought them all for our collection.
